# One‑Sheet (Trade Data)

**Strategy:** {{ strategy\_name }}
**Timeframe:** {{ timeframe }}
**Instrument(s):** {{ instruments }}
**Run Date:** {{ run\_date }}
**Session Basis:** New York time (ET) RTH 09:30–16:00
**Initial Capital (float):** \${{ initial\_capital }}
**Commission (RT / contract):** \${{ commission\_per\_round\_trip }}
**Point Value:** \${{ point\_value }} per point per contract

> Values are produced by the lean analyzer and written to `metrics.json`. Replace the double‑braced placeholders with values from that file (same keys), or wire your script to auto‑render this template.

---

## Headline KPIs

* **Net Profit:** \${{ net\_profit }}
* **Total Return:** {{ total\_return\_pct }}%
* **Win Rate:** {{ win\_rate\_pct }}%
* **Profit Factor:** {{ profit\_factor }}
* **Max Drawdown:** \${{ max\_drawdown\_dollars }} ({{ max\_drawdown\_pct }}%)
* **CAGR:** {{ CAGR }}

---

## Performance (returns & consistency)

| Metric                    |                                  Result | Definition / Formula                               |          |   |
| ------------------------- | --------------------------------------: | -------------------------------------------------- | -------- | - |
| Net Profit (\$)           |                     \${{ net\_profit }} | Σ(NetPLᵢ)                                          |          |   |
| Total Return (%)          |               {{ total\_return\_pct }}% | (Net Profit ÷ Initial Capital) × 100               |          |   |
| Average Monthly Return    |             {{ avg\_monthly\_return }}% | mean(Monthly equity % change)                      |          |   |
| CAGR                      |                              {{ CAGR }} | (Ending Equity ÷ Initial Capital)^(365 ÷ Days) − 1 |          |   |
| Profit Factor             |                    {{ profit\_factor }} | (Σ profits) ÷                                      | Σ losses |   |
| Win Rate (%)              |                   {{ win\_rate\_pct }}% | (# wins ÷ total trades) × 100                      |          |   |
| Avg Win (\$)              |               \${{ avg\_win\_dollars }} | mean(NetPL                                         | NetPL>0) |   |
| Avg Loss (\$)             |              \${{ avg\_loss\_dollars }} | mean(NetPL                                         | NetPL<0) |   |
| Avg Win (pts / contract)  |   {{ avg\_win\_points\_per\_contract }} | NetPL ÷ (point\_value ×                            | Qty      | ) |
| Avg Loss (pts / contract) |  {{ avg\_loss\_points\_per\_contract }} | NetPL ÷ (point\_value ×                            | Qty      | ) |
| Expectancy per Trade (\$) | \${{ expectancy\_per\_trade\_dollars }} | mean(NetPLᵢ)                                       |          |   |

---

## Risk (drawdowns & risk‑adjusted)

| Metric                      |                           Result | Definition / Formula         |
| --------------------------- | -------------------------------: | ---------------------------- |
| Max Drawdown (\$)           |   \${{ max\_drawdown\_dollars }} | max(peak − Equity)           |
| Max Drawdown (%)            |        {{ max\_drawdown\_pct }}% | min(Equity ÷ peak − 1) × 100 |
| Average Drawdown (%)        |        {{ avg\_drawdown\_pct }}% | mean(Drawdownₜ) × 100        |
| Recovery Factor             |           {{ recovery\_factor }} | Net Profit ÷ Max DD (\$)     |
| Sharpe (per‑trade proxy)    |  {{ per\_trade\_sharpe\_proxy }} | mean(rᵢ) ÷ stdev(rᵢ)         |
| Sortino (per‑trade proxy)   | {{ per\_trade\_sortino\_proxy }} | mean(rᵢ) ÷ stdev(min(rᵢ,0))  |
| Largest Winning Trade (\$)  |  \${{ largest\_winning\_trade }} | max(NetPLᵢ)                  |
| Largest Losing Trade (\$)   |   \${{ largest\_losing\_trade }} | min(NetPLᵢ)                  |
| Volatility of Trade Returns |    {{ vol\_of\_trade\_returns }} | stdev(per‑trade returns)     |

---

## Trade Analytics (behavior & cadence)

| Metric                     |                                        Result |
| -------------------------- | --------------------------------------------: |
| Number of Trades           |                             {{ num\_trades }} |
| Long Trades                |                              {{ num\_longs }} |
| Short Trades               |                             {{ num\_shorts }} |
| Avg Holding Time (minutes) |                      {{ avg\_hold\_minutes }} |
| Session Tags (ET)          | Overnight / Pre / Open / Midday / Late / Post |

> For session‑level slicing, use `trades_enriched.csv` (column **Session**).

